2008-11-09  Michael Weber  <michaelw@foldr.org>

	* Released version 0.8.0

	* cl-dot.lisp (textify,print-key-value): allow labels to be
	aligned.  Patch adapted from Nikodemus Siivola
	<nikodemus@random-state.net>.

